{"tid":757544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【立場逆轉】「中國老朋友」基辛格獻計 教特朗普聯俄制中","createTime":"2018-07-27T02:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T13:27:11.000Z","uid":13663,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd0222c1968ab0e52efa16cecc79edd00dac25a","tid":757544,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:54:01.000Z","msg":"【立場逆轉】「中國老朋友」基辛格獻計 教特朗普聯俄制中<br />\n1小時前3.6K<br />\n即時國際<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n美國前國務卿基辛格（Henry Kissinger）在以往冷戰時期，一直主張「聯中抗蘇」，故素有「中國老朋友」之稱。但《The Daily Beast》引述消息人士報道，基辛格與總統特朗普曾多次私下會面，完全顛倒昔日觀點，向特朗普獻計美國可「聯俄制中」，以阻止崛起的中國。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述白宮及國會消息人士稱，基辛格的主張獲特朗普身邊一些高級顧問接納，同意應與莫斯科建立更親密關係遏制北京。但特朗普對俄羅斯總統普京的「順從」，引發國內不少抨擊及批評「叛國」的聲音，令計劃難度大增。消息指基辛格強調聯俄並非最終目標，只是一個改造中國權力架構的長遠策略，與白宮前首席智囊班農（Steve Bannon）強調必須盡快應對來自中國及阿拉伯地區的威脅有所不同。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士形容基辛格改變以往主張的動機，較諸班農「更誠實及光榮」，「（基辛格）並不主張與俄羅斯建立夥伴關係，但他堅持17年來全球反恐戰佔據了太多時間及焦點，而他深信會（與中國）有巨大權力鬥爭。」因此雖多位白宮高層官員認同俄羅斯將是對抗中國的「有用籌碼」，但並非所有人都接受這個構思，因此目前只能列入「考慮」之列。"},{"pid":"5bfc1d4923d206d6eabe07d98f6ff176a3594b40","tid":757544,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"白宮及國家安全委員會官員拒絕評論報道，基辛格辦公室亦未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n基辛格一向不被歸類為對華鷹派，眾所周知他可以直接與中國國家主席習近平通電話，而自習近平去年倡導「一帶一路」主張後，基辛格亦曾評價對亞洲地區會有正面影響。<br />\n<br />\n但基辛格同時亦非「恐俄者」，他多年來曾先後17次與俄羅斯總統普京會面，亦多次提出華府應該與莫斯科建立更佳的合作關係。特朗普早前與普京在芬蘭舉行峯會後，基辛格便曾說：「這是一個必須舉行的會議，我已提議多年」，他亦曾就俄羅斯被指干涉總統大選發言，質疑俄國干擾大選目的何在。<br />\n<br />\n自兩年前總選大選起，基辛格與特朗普至少曾會面3次，消息人士指，特朗普在總統大選期間，他的幕後已曾討論親近俄羅斯、日本、菲律賓、印度及中東國家，藉此牽制中國。<br />\n<br />\n《The Daily Beast》"},{"pid":"87c5a5df38ab76b92c8b5ce9b0fca8536088c6cf","tid":757544,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6d2a950301984190250b655224d8de2ad4abca","tid":757544,"uid":95497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"用中國最中意嘅遠交近攻對付中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307321bcd44d606c00ddea37a2884bc18e443601","tid":757544,"uid":177047,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"支國BFF 呀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f9cfd1ea2f23950cb640f3210d15db461253b3","tid":757544,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b8fb4cdf16a7a39f90094a996368b468360846","tid":757544,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:00:26.000Z","msg":"聯日好過啦"},{"pid":"57f131385ade0383bc239b599cb53a2beaf5c859","tid":757544,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af061f148bfc635c09359b1aadcd0cd90250cf94","tid":757544,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"俄狗同支那咪又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c68ff56bb16373e2a8d54c6eb7377be1e1ce17","tid":757544,"uid":43009,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af061f148bfc635c09359b1aadcd0cd90250cf94","tid":757544,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"俄狗同支那咪又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"支那陰濕啲 中意搞小動作<br />\n俄佬明刀明槍"},{"pid":"9944c6423627fe50bc9a3632f6853448305525f2","tid":757544,"uid":4138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af061f148bfc635c09359b1aadcd0cd90250cf94","tid":757544,"uid":36178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T12:26:30.000Z","msg":"俄狗同支那咪又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T14:23:07.000Z","msg":"所以冇永遠嘅朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78c5cb7e0559a1c5e01ed3e782b838348fba889","tid":757544,"uid":84622,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俄狗同支那咪又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>支那陰濕啲 中意搞小動作<br />\n俄佬明刀明槍</blockquote><br />\n干預美國大選都叫明刀明槍？<br />\n搵人係fb開page觸發種族予盾都叫明刀明槍？"},{"pid":"dbae27f64d4c5b3d8161b99cf12328edb72294b4","tid":757544,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"【即時文摘】一注獨中（陶傑）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180728/58492453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58492453&d=rPk%2BqPz8NcK6ymllK2Cm5Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0cef2580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58492453&h=b351f0e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180728/58492453</a><br />\n<br />\n社交媒體盛行，許多人渴望成為所謂KOL，亦「意見領袖」。時有小朋友來問：怎樣可以做KOL。<br />\n<br />\n我答：要對世界趨勢，先瞻先覺；預測世界巨變，要有「一注獨中」的未卜先知之能。<br />\n譬如二○一七年二月二十六日，我在「壹週刊」之每周專欄預測：美國政界元老基辛格，將會向川普面授機宜，叫狂人總統聯俄制中。<br />\n<br />\n我當日這樣寫：「可以大膽假設：基辛格晚年要重組世界秩序。美國資金正尋求撤出中國，大陸勞工成本增加，出的多，進的少。基辛格的公關公司，也像香港的電視傳媒，形勢變幻，到了盈利的水尾。如果我是他，大丈夫此時不棄商歸政，秉承他五十多年前的巨著『權力平衡論』（Balance of Power），發揮餘熱，叱咤風雲，完成聯俄制中，再主宰一次世界，又更待何時？」<br />\n<br />\n一年半之後，此一預言獲得驗證：美國新聞網站Daily Beast，於二○一八年七月二十五日「引述消息人士」：前國務卿基辛格，曾向川普提出「聯俄抗中」建議。基辛格也曾向川普女婿，提出同樣建議。<br />\n<br />\n此一注獨中，只須了解猶太人性與中國民族性，中國的薄熙來春風得意之時，請基辛格去重慶觀賞紅歌匯演，基辛格VIP第一排，看完大讚。<br />\n<br />\n我看了這一幕，心中大讚基辛格不但智商高，也了解中國人的心理性格。中國人喜歡洋人讚譽，其「百年屈辱」之心理壓抑自卑，渴望得到西方白人向他們伸出大拇指。基辛格令中國人笑逐顏開，遂芝麻開門，基辛格牽線，替美國公司說客公關賺大錢。<br />\n<br />\n二十年來我聽見許多中國的學者、國際關係專家，尊基辛格為中國人民的老朋友，熱呼之為「基老爺子」，我心中都暗笑。<br />\n<br />\n革命紅二代精英，好朋友薄熙來，曾榮獲基老爺子讚譽是中國理想的未來領袖。也有一些半吊子知識份子看不過眼，覺得他擦鞋。不錯，基老爺子的巨著「中國論」（On China），都在給中國人臉上貼金，貼得中國人笑呵呵。<br />\n<br />\n當然，也不是我一人威水，去年預言基辛格叫川普聯俄制中之此一論文，在壹週刊發表，壹週刊的老闆先創此商場，供我賣貨，更加威水，但香港人卻逼其忍痛出售壹週刊，未免短視，好在終物歸原主了。<br />\n<br />\n哈哈。But anyway，中國文人多渴望做國師。基辛格不是庸俗的「國師」，他只是一個高人。若欲為成功人士，當學基辛格。"},{"pid":"8534f05cba79936f1dbe6ec829a68cee8fd23047","tid":757544,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c78c5cb7e0559a1c5e01ed3e782b838348fba889","tid":757544,"uid":84622,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>俄狗同支那咪又係一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>支那陰濕啲 中意搞小動作<br />\n俄佬明刀明槍</blockquote><br />\n干預美國大選都叫明刀明槍？<br />\n搵人係fb開page觸發種族予盾都叫明刀明槍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「（基辛格）<strong>並不主張與俄羅斯建立夥伴關係</strong>，但他堅持17年來全球反恐戰佔據了太多時間及焦點，而他深信會（與中國）有巨大權力鬥爭。」</span><br />\n<br />\nON9仔<br />\n政治冇永遠朋友敵人，邊個威脅大咪打邊個lor"},{"pid":"3c0393a2dd09f97530cc72fd3f04551eac0ca977","tid":757544,"uid":75656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/195416_5b5b9e0398827223c50d2a7da0a37d70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F195416_5b5b9e0398827223c50d2a7da0a37d70.png&h=4d6b9a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37fa2be09785e3db2b6a8f91190a60e3b0cb528c","tid":757544,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:56:17.000Z","msg":"美國要frd 都同白種人frd 先，幾時到支那黃狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eec1fa6c328f78d7323d03bb58f7f3f7e726139","tid":757544,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"猶太人當年畀人送去集中營唔系無緣無故(no offence)"},{"pid":"b8caf35df5d1add71597f900430d192920876f68","tid":757544,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6eec1fa6c328f78d7323d03bb58f7f3f7e726139","tid":757544,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"猶太人當年畀人送去集中營唔系無緣無故(no offence)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"猶太人 被人屠殺, 係因為佢地太高質, 各國眼紅佢地<br />\n<br />\n支那人 被人屠殺, 係因為佢地太劣質, 犯眾憎"},{"pid":"7ffc65e046f92238053ff1099db252d6dc9cfc2d","tid":757544,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8caf35df5d1add71597f900430d192920876f68","tid":757544,"uid":53705,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6eec1fa6c328f78d7323d03bb58f7f3f7e726139","tid":757544,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:06:11.000Z","msg":"猶太人當年畀人送去集中營唔系無緣無故(no offence)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"猶太人 被人屠殺, 係因為佢地太高質, 各國眼紅佢地<br />\n<br />\n支那人 被人屠殺, 係因為佢地太劣質, 犯眾憎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15564695ef103cde0554840b3414cff1c82f2c97","tid":757544,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ffc65e046f92238053ff1099db252d6dc9cfc2d","tid":757544,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8caf35df5d1add71597f900430d192920876f68","tid":757544,"uid":53705,"like":7,"d